Package: simeis
Version: 0.1.3
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Dreyves DOUKANDA <gilbert.famillemarros@gmail.com>
Depends: cmatrix
Description: Simeis space game server
 Simeis is a multiplayer space exploration game server.
 Players interact with the game through a REST API on port 8080.
 Each player controls a ship and can explore the galaxy, trade resources,
 and upgrade their crew.
